Requirement
===========
1- Terraform
2- Azure Account
3- Azure cli
4- VScode
5- git
6- shell - bash,powershell
------------------------------------------
Installing terrafom in windows
1- download terraform zip and extract
2- copy the extracted binary file to desired terraform folder c:\devops\terraform
3- search for advanced system setting link and add c:\devops\terraform in environment variable path
install azure cli , VScode and Git
4- Verify installation from cmd by running terraform --help
===============================================
Installing Terraform in Linux
1- wget terraform zip file
2- unzip terraform.zip
3- mv terraform /usr/local/bin
4- Verify installation from cmd by running terraform --help
5- install azure cli  curl -sL https://aka.ms/installAzureCLIDeb |sudo bash
6- install git apt-get install git
7- snap install --classic-doce  for VScode
